        p.extra-info Pour a very small amount.

      article.item
        img(src='assets/img/food/wasabi.jpeg')
        p.caption Wasabi
        p.extra-info extremely hot. Recover from too much by breathing through the nose.
        p.extra-info Not to be mixed with soy sauce.

      article.item
